
Node Js

    It is a platform to Run Javascript
	
	Node  -  Node Run time
	
	Npm - Node Package manager
	
	
Anything which you build/develop using node is called node package

To manage your node app/service  we will use node package manager (npm)

NPM -

   We can download dependencies[libraries needed for your project]
   We can download utilities[compiler/transpiler/code generator/ Test
   case runner]
   We can publish our projects in public/private repositories
   We can build/run/test our node applications
   We can Run Some development related tasks [testing/linting/build scripts/
   packaging]